## Project Overview
Medure is a healthcare/pharma domain application deployed using an
end-to-end DevOps CI/CD pipeline.

## Tools & Technologies
- AWS EC2
- Jenkins
- Docker & DockerHub
- Kubernetes
- Ansible
- Git & GitHub
- Linux

## CI/CD Workflow
1. Developer pushes code to GitHub
2. Jenkins triggers pipeline
3. Application is built using Maven
4. Docker image is created and pushed to DockerHub
5. Kubernetes deploys application using Deployment & Service

## Kubernetes Deployment
- Deployment with 1 replica
- Service type: NodePort

## Output
Application is accessible using:
http://<Master-Public-IP>:<NodePort>

## Conclusion
This project demonstrates real-time DevOps practices including CI/CD,
containerization, orchestration, and automation.
